text: Tini ratake dine prabesa karana ebam dinake prabesa karana rate, tini surya o camdake karechena niyamadhina; pratyeke paribhramana kare eka nirdista samaya paryanta. Tini'i allah tomadera raba. Adhipatya tamra'i. Ara tomara tamra paribarte yaderake daka tara to khejura amtira abaranera'o adhikari naya
